No decorators, but fast-check has add-ons to various test frameworks. E.g. if you use Vitest you can write:    import { test, fc } from '@fast-check/vitest'
    test.prop([fc.array(fc.double())])('sort is correct', (lst) => {
      expect(lst).toEqual(lst.toSorted())
    })

